An Act relative to the definition of livestock.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 SECTION 17. Section 1A of chapter 128 of the General Laws is hereby amending by
2 inserting, at the end of said section, the following:-
3 This section shall not apply to the raising of dogs or cats for breeding, the raising or
4 keeping of dogs or cats for other commercial use, or to the commercial grooming of dogs or cats.
